    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Quaralia",
      "JAVIER\nFROM WAKE ISLAND\nFlight Breakfast\nFresh Orange Juice\nChilled Frust\nFluffy Bacon Omelette\nToust Triangles\nBastter\nJelly\nCoffee\nTea\nMAk\nBreakfast Muffins\nThe President\nPAN AMERICAN WORLD AIRWAYS",
      "Caroomba, city of the Blue\nMountains in New South Wales,\noffers a trio of eurious crags.\nStanding 1000 feet above the\nJamieson Valley, these \"Three\nSisters' command a sweep of\nred and ochre cliffs . .. mist-\ndeepened bowls of cobalt blue.\nPen American serves the\nSouth Pacific through Nandi\nin the Fiji Islands, Sydney in\nAustralia and through Auckland\nin New Zealand\nThis wens is one of a complete set, suitable for framing,\nwhich may be okaixed by writing to: Serwee Manager,\nPacife- Alaska Dicision, Pan American World Airways,\nInc.. International Airport. San Francisco, California.",
      "dale.\nWrillen aboard the Pan\nFlying Clipper:\nen roule from\n•Clipper."
